        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>Henrik Sonnergård is my name. The 'å' hints that I am from Scandinavia, more precisely from Sweden. I studied natural science in high school and are now working with web and graphic design projects for a small company, everything from digital to print. Apart from that I work on my own web projects while earning more experience in the field. I think my parents have given me the ability to be interested in many and very different things. Astronomy, biology and chemistry are very close to my heart, as well as other fields such as sailing, mechanics and even carpentry.</p>
